</p>

<blockquote>
<table>
<tr>
    <td>Name:</td>    
    <td>Upamanyu CHATTERJEE</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Nationality:</td>
    <td>India</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td>Born:</td>    
    <td>1959</td>
</tr>
</table>
<br>

<font size="-1">
<ul>
	<li>Attended St. Stephen's College, Delhi
	<li>Joined the Indian Administrative Service in 1983
</ul>
</font>

</blockquote>

